Interface ApiRoleSourcePlugin

All Superinterfaces:
InternalPlugin, IStartablePlugin, Remote
All Known Implementing Classes:

public interface ApiRoleSourcePlugin extends IStartablePlugin
Plugin point that represents a source for ApiRoles that can load a role by name

  • Method Details

    • getRole

      ApiRole getRole(String roleName)
      Loads the ApiRole that corresponds to the given role name. If no such ApiRole was found, will fallback to loading the ApiRole that corresponds to the English (US) name of the role with the given role name. Returns an EmptyApiRole if neither the given role name nor the English (US) name of that role corresponds to any ApiRole.

    • getRoles

      default List<ApiRole> getRoles()
      Returns a list of all roles The default implementation returns an empty unmodifiable list
